            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2186.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>creamy cauliflower pasta</strong> to an<strong> oven-proof dish </strong></p>\n<p>Top with the <strong>cheesy breadcrumbs </strong></p>\n<p>Sprinkle over the <strong>bacon lardons</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until the bacon is cooked and the breadcrumbs are golden</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2186.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
